com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306

Class ProductTemplateTargeting

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.dfp.v201306.ProductTemplateTargeting
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ProductTemplateTargeting
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains targeting criteria for ProductTemplate objects. Proposal line items created from products of this template will have this criteria added to ProposalLineItem.targeting.
